Large Group Quoting and Enrollment Enhancements

Use enhanced flows to rate large group quotes and enroll members in plans. Delete census members in bulk and enable customers to self-enroll by using new and enhanced services.

Automate the Cleanup of Asynchronous Rating Data​
Save time and effort by using custom settings and a scheduled batch job to remove unnecessary large group quoting and enrollment rating data.

Complete Enrollment at Scale With an Enhanced Enrollment Flow
Enroll up to 10,000 members at a time with up to 30 distinct plan choices for each member.

Quickly Delete All Members of the Group Census
Reduce time and effort to delete up to 10,000 members each with up to five plans and up to five coverages selected per plan.

Rate Large Group Plans More Efficiently
Use the updated version of the Generate Census Rating flow and the Finish Processing Census Rating flow to rate more plans at a time.

Rate More Large Group Benefits Products at a Time
Summary-based products are now rated asynchronously to support rating more large group benefits products at a time.

Save Agents Time by Using Customer Self-Enrollment
Enable customers to view and select one or more eligible plans along with optional coverages, and then rate and enroll.

Quickly Find Large Group Census Members During Enrollment and Quoting
Use the Search box on Enrollment Census and Quote Census Lightning web components to quickly find census member details.
